    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast. Every aspect of this motorcar has been maintained to the highest standards, featuring a flawless exterior finish and a pristine interior that retains its original luster. Mechanically superlative and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, it offers an uncompromised driving experience for those who demand nothing less than excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this absolute stunner. Honestly, it\u2019s like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014I\u2019ve babied this car from day one and it shows! Everything is in pristine shape, inside and out. It\u2019s such a smooth, reliable ride, and I\u2019m genuinely sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. If you\u2019re looking for a dream car that\u2019s been cared for with a lot of love, this is the one for you! Drop me a message if you want to take a look!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a museum-grade E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. The S65 V8 remains the centerpiece, delivering a linear power band up to its 8,400 RPM redline with crisp throttle response. This specimen features a meticulous service history, including preventative rod bearing replacement and upgraded throttle actuators. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission offers lightning-fast shifts, while the M Variable Differential Lock ensures maximum lateral grip. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing a broad range of damping characteristics from compliant to track-stiff. The exterior retains its factory depth with no imperfections, and the interior bolsters show zero compression. Zero subframe fatigue, no fluid seepage, and a flawless DME report confirm its mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2021 Sedan. Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. Zero accidents. Complete service records. Clean title. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom-ready condition. Every inch of the exterior gleams with a deep, mirror-like finish, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating and kept exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats are supple and free of any wear, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is flawless. It has been serviced strictly at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive file of records to prove its pampered history. There are zero scratches, zero dings, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been treated as a prized possession rather than just a mode of transport.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
