      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary automotive specimen, maintained to the most exacting standards. This vehicle is in pristine condition, boasting a flawless exterior finish and a meticulously preserved interior that retains its original luster. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets the requirements of the most discerning collector. This is a rare opportunity to secure a vehicle of peerless quality and uncompromising integrity.",
      "price": 43500.0,
